sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Agent Runtime
    participant S as SidecarProxy
    participant I as ToolInterceptor
    participant E as OPAEvaluator
    participant A as AuditEmitter

    C->>S: JSONL request over Unix socket
    S->>I: intercept(tool_name, params, session_id)
    I->>E: evaluate(ToolCallEvent)
    E-->>I: PolicyDecision
    I-->>S: PolicyDecision
    S->>A: emit(event, decision)
    A-->>S: return immediately
    S-->>C: {"action":"forward|drop","decision":...}

    Note over S: Malformed JSON -> fail-open {"action":"forward","error":...}
